{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/patchwork-komik-horor-romantis-yang-bisa-bikin-deg-degan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Patchwork, Komik Horor Romantis yang Bisa Bikin Deg-Degan!","content":"<p>Kebayang gak sih kalau kamu ketemu seorang perempuan yang kepalanya bisa lepas dari tubuhnya? Pastinya hal seperti itu mustahil terjadi di dunia nyata, secara horor dan pastinya menakutkan kalau memang benar-benar ada. Namun, cerita ber-<em>genre </em>horor seperti ini selalu bisa membuat siapapun yang membaca ikut di bawa penasaran.</p>\n<p>Memang, apapun yang berbau horor, biasanya selalu identik dengan hal-hal yang menakutkan. Namun, gimana kalau <em>genre</em> horor dan romantis digabungkan? Nah, kayaknya <b>k a i r n n</b> berhasil menggabungkan keduanya ke dalam sebuah komik yang saat ini lagi <em>hitz </em>abis,<em> </em>Patchwork.</p>\n<p>Bercerita mengenai seorang perempuan bernama Patchwork yang menginginkan kehidupan normal selayaknya manusia biasa. Namun, hal ini gak mudah untuk ia dapatkan karena ternyata dia mempunyai rahasia berupa keanehan pada tubuhnya. Menurut kalian, bisa gak, Patchwork menjalani kehidupan normal dan juga dicintai?</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/spooky-sweetheart-jatuh-cinta-dengan-hantu-cantik/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Spooky Sweetheart, Jatuh Cinta dengan Hantu Cantik?</a></strong></p>\n<p>Yuk, kita kenalan dulu sama beberapa karakter penting dari komik Patchwork. Ada cowok ganteng dan cewek cantik yang meramaikan juga, lho!</p>\n<h2>Para Karakter Patchwork</h2>\n<h3><strong>Patchwork</strong></h3>\n<p>Nah, ini dia karakter utama komik yang punya nama sama yaitu, <em>Patchwork</em>. Patchwork sendiri bekerja sebagai pengasuh anak-anak di sebuah tempat penitipan anak. Kamu bisa memanggil dia dengan sebutan &#8220;Patchi&#8221; nih.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45161\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45161\" data-attachment-id=\"45161\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/patchwork-komik-horor-romantis-yang-bisa-bikin-deg-degan/attachment/ptchwk7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk7.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45161 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk7.jpg\" alt=\"Patchwork\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45161\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Manis ya, apalagi dengan rambut berwarna merah menambah kesan manisnya dan terlihat menakutkan di saat bersamaan. Patchi juga punya rahasia loh, dimana bagian tubuhnya bisa terlepas dan harus dijahit untuk mengabungkannya. Sesuaidengan namanya yang berarti kain perca, makanya harus dijahit, deh. Hii, cantik-cantik tapi seram ya!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45157\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45157\" data-attachment-id=\"45157\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/patchwork-komik-horor-romantis-yang-bisa-bikin-deg-degan/attachment/ptchwk3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk3.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45157 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk3.jpg\" alt=\"Patchwork patchy\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45157\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<h3><strong>Ein</strong></h3>\n<p>Mahasiswa hukum berusia 20 tahun ini, menjadi orang yang menemukan rahasia dari Patchi. Saat itu, mereka tidak sengaja bertabrakan dan kepala Patchi lepas. Kebayang gak sih kalau tiba-tiba ketemu orang tapi kepalanya lepas? Pastinya terkejut dan takut, sama nih seperti Ein saat bertemu dengan Patchi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45156\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45156\" data-attachment-id=\"45156\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/patchwork-komik-horor-romantis-yang-bisa-bikin-deg-degan/attachment/ptchwk2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk2.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45156 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk2.jpg\" alt=\"Patchwork ein\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45156\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Meski terlihat bahagia, Ein mengalami masa-masa sulit semenjak meninggalnya adiknya dua tahun lalu. Nah, akibat kesendirian ini, Ein pun menjadi anak yang nakal bahkan jadi pemalak.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45158\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45158\" data-attachment-id=\"45158\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/patchwork-komik-horor-romantis-yang-bisa-bikin-deg-degan/attachment/ptchwk4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk4.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45158 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk4.jpg\" alt=\"Patchwork ein\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45158\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/wendigo-perjalanan-reuni-yang-berakhir-bencana/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wendigo, Perjalanan Reuni yang Berakhir Bencana</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Jeremiah</strong></h3>\n<p>Polisi berusia 28 tahun ini merupakan polisi yang menangani kasus pembunuhan Surgam, loh! Ganteng kan? Eh, tapi dia punya seorang adik yang dekat dengan Ein nih.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45160\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45160\" data-attachment-id=\"45160\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/patchwork-komik-horor-romantis-yang-bisa-bikin-deg-degan/attachment/ptchwk6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk6.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45160 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk6.jpg\" alt=\"Patchwork jeremiah\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45160\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Sudah beberapa tahun ini dia berusaha untuk menangkap Surgam, namun belum berhasil. Malahan dia pernah terluka dalam usaha pengejaran Surgam ini. Kira-kira apakah dia akan berhasil, ya?</p>\n<h3><strong>Judaria</strong></h3>\n<p>Teman masa kecil Ein yang mengetahui semua permasalahan dalam hidup Ein. Ia memiliki janji untuk dapat menemukan Surgam, pembunuh adik Ein. Judaria atau yang biasa dipanggil &#8220;Judy&#8221; juga merupakan adik dari Jeremiah. loh.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45159\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45159\" data-attachment-id=\"45159\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/patchwork-komik-horor-romantis-yang-bisa-bikin-deg-degan/attachment/ptchwk5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk5.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45159 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk5.jpg\" alt=\"Patchwork judaria\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45159\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan rambut pendek berwarna hitam,  Judy terlihat manis dan juga misterius. Selain itu, dia juga memiliki rahasia tersembuny. Kira-kira rahasia apa, ya?</p>\n<h3><strong>Surgam</strong></h3>\n<p>Kalau yang ini, pembunuh berantai yang sudah menghantui kota selama beberapa tahun terakhir. Sampai saat ini identitas sebenarnya belum juga diketahui. Wajar aja, soalnya meski telah dikejar polisi, Surgam mampu untuk melarikan diri.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45155\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45155\" data-attachment-id=\"45155\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/patchwork-komik-horor-romantis-yang-bisa-bikin-deg-degan/attachment/ptchwk1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: CIAYO Comics&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-45155 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk1.jpg\" alt=\"Patchwork surgam\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/ptchwk1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45155\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Kira-kira siapa ya Surgam ini? Dan apa hubungannya dengan <em>Patchwork</em>? Yuk, cari tau dengan ikuti terus ceritanya hanya di <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/patchwork\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics</a>.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b2fd685c-6457-5895-b283-8f07ae46bf72"}}}